—ظTarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/is-not-empty.mdظ@fc3913ecd57d1e4431d5f13d314ecd9aa01c543793288abd00e544a3ef09fc3f³title: is-not-empty‘¨Examplesع4Check if a string is empty
