false

```
Check if a list is empty
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [] | is-not-empty
false

```
Check if more than one column are empty
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[meal size]; [arepa small] [taco '']] | is-not-empty meal size
true

```
